TESTCASE1:
 Users password is incorrect so the program would ask them to try again (until they enter the right password
 or exit the program

TESTCASE2:
 User enters correct information, updates balance by depositing some money and then exits the program. The
 program will return the new balance back into atm class (so that her new balance will be saved)

TESTCASE3:
 User enters deposit and then withdraws but enters a wrong value (non number), the program will tell the user
 that their input is invalid and that they have to enter again

TESTCASE4:
 User enters a name/account that is not in the system so the account will continue asking them to check name
 and/or account number or to exit.

TESTCASE5:
 Secret option hacker on the menu which will print out all of the information to user
